Berlusconi, Tremonti to Meet on Austerity Plan, Repubblica Says

-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-08-28T10:01:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-28/berlusconi-tremonti-to-meet-on-austerity-plan-repubblica-says.html
Italian Prime Minister  Silvio Berlusconi  and Finance Minister  Giulio Tremonti  are meeting
tomorrow to find an agreement on austerity measures, daily  la
Repubblica  reported, without saying how it got the information.  Umberto Bossi, leader of Italy’s Northern League and
Berlusconi’s closest political ally, will also attend the
meeting in Arcore, near Milan, Repubblica said. Measures
discussed will include raising the value-added tax, extra taxes
on higher earners and pension reform, Repubblica said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at   kwong11@bloomberg.net  